#: guide/en/chapter4.txt:12
msgid "Delete a chapter"
msgstr ""

#: guide/en/chapter4.txt:18
msgid ""
"To delete a chapter, you can do so from the CourseEditor. Simply find the "
"section where the chapter is present and edit it. You will be able to delete "
"the chapter by pressing on the \"trash\" icon."
msgstr ""

