#: guide/en/chapter4.txt:20
msgid "Move a chapter"
msgstr ""

#: guide/en/chapter4.txt:24
msgid ""
"To move a chapter within the same section, you can simply use the drag and "
"drop elements.\n"
"We don't yet support moving chapters within different sections."
msgstr ""
